104
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,640
to sell the land to Lin Corporation.

105
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,480
But I refused it.

106
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,040
Because I found

107
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,680
something wrong with that piece of land.

108
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:26,000
