134
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,000
I...

135
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:18,480
I...

136
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,200
As the executive director
of the company,

137
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,640
